Package ch.mazluc.data

Interface Data

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<Object>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Table, Tuple
public interface Data extends Iterable<Object>

Represents a data structure. A data structure is a collection of values. It is an extension of the Iterable interface.

See Repo for more: GitHub
